{"id": 2511, "genre": 1000, "title": "除了点赞，你在社交媒体上还有哪些表达认可的方式？", "description": "“点赞”已经没办法表达我的喜爱之情了，至少也是“转评赞+打赏”起步。（题图来自：iStock © CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 8711, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201809051616490fdHO5Nk3sRtGJhg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-12T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4663, "title": "除了点赞，你在社交媒体上还有哪些表达认可的方式？", "content": "除了点赞，你在社交媒体上还有哪些表达认可的方式？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 297472, "content": "读完正文之后，继续看“阅读原文”里面的超链接", "image": "img/option/option/20180905192338mQKinqCvZkEtFWus.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297479, "content": "给商品/服务好评的时候，除了打分还会顺带写几句话", "image": "img/option/option/20180905192326cfeglZiFjJ86bEKs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297480, "content": "加好友/关注之后，设置为置顶/星标/特别关注", "image": "img/option/option/20180905192246Y6NewqB7maxJZFK5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297481, "content": "把图标放到手机第一屏，并且选择“打开推送”", "image": "img/option/option/201809051922073eHjBrvnUfXG5lhQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298326, "content": "看到有意思的微博，除了点赞，还会@别的朋友来看", "image": "img/option/option/20180912104446YAd5MwSu2CWsKlxb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298329, "content": "在朋友圈最高评价不是点赞，而是一串哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20180912104506wUhaEDAl134pviBg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298332, "content": "对“特别想让大家都知道”的好作品，大号转发并安利", "image": "img/option/option/20180912110108f2dcrS64ZybCUxpv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297465, "content": "认真写很长一段（不带任何表情包/抖机灵的）评论", "image": "img/option/option/20180905193231R4GYclCDk5dhZbfg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297466, "content": "先读完全文，再放进收藏夹", "image": "img/option/option/20180905193155oUXmLe6Fpc0aY9WT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297467, "content": "点开微信推送下方的小广告以示支持", "image": "img/option/option/201809051931057WXg8DAGpYncj5Uk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297470, "content": "给文章作者打赏", "image": "img/option/option/20180905192545yEYfnrdsHm9bIP1p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}